00:10:29,338 --> 00:10:33,425
First thing we did was
went to Manny's Music, man.

160
00:10:33,508 --> 00:10:35,469
Manny's Music!

161
00:10:38,930 --> 00:10:42,351
<i>BOBBY: I bought a Rickenbacker guitar
