1255
01:30:10,489 --> 01:30:12,616
<i>He convinced us.</i>

1256
01:30:16,703 --> 01:30:19,331
Not only did he convince us, but he...

1257
01:30:21,208 --> 01:30:26,839
He inspired us, because we had
the chance to change the name.

1258
01:30:28,715 --> 01:30:34,888
